'''I Khangeri le Chache Yesu''' si yek mesti khangeri kerdili ando [[Beijing]], [[China]], ando [[1917]]to bersh. O akanutno alosardo shero le mashkarthemutne kidipnaske le KhChJ si o predikatoro Yung-Ji Lin. Akana si opretele 1.5 milyonurya pativale ande 6 [[Barodvip|barodvipurya]]. I khangeri si o kinezikano kotor le [[Pentikostalipen]]sko andar o [[Kristiyanipen]]. I khangeri patyal ando [[pentikostalikano yekipen]] ([[IYesuesko-anav doktrina]]).

